l\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y nh\u00e0m ch\u00e1n cho nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u01b0a th\u00edch d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n. H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng l\u00e0m r\u00f5 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 th\u00f4ng qua nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Senegal vs Ba Lan.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/tuong-thuat-ba-lan-vs-senegal-463-188940.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/tuong-thuat-ba-lan-vs-senegal.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/tuong-thuat-ba-lan-vs-senegal-463-188940.html\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Ba Lan vs Senegal 22h00 ng\u00e0y 19/6 (World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\n<span>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Ba Lan vs Senegal: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 xem tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ba Lan vs Senegal b\u1ea3ng H World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 22h00...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<em>Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u: </em>Ba Lan vs Senegal<br>\r\n<em>Th\u1eddi gian: </em>22h ng\u00e0y 19/6<br>\r\n<em>\u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m:</em> Otkrytiye Arena (Moskva)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>TLCA c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn: </em>Ba Lan 1.00*0:1/4*0.95 Senegal<br>\r\n<em>TBT c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn:</em> Nhi\u1ec1u 0.96*2*0.97 \u00cdt<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Senegal vs Ba Lan v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n v\u00e0ng tr\u00ean Bongda24hvn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Senegal vs Ba Lan v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n v\u00e0ng tr\u00ean Bongda24hvn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/nhan-dinh-senegal-vs-ba-lan-va-du-doan-senegal-vs-ba-lan.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Senegal vs Ba Lan 22h ng\u00e0y 19/6</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\n\u00cdt b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u1ea1i l\u00ean ng\u00f4i (U 2)</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n14 trong t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 16 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u00f4i qua. C\u00f3 t\u1edbi 9 tr\u1eadn trong \u0111\u00f3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u1edf xu\u1ed1ng, t\u1ee9c chi\u1ebfm 64%. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Harry Kane \u1edf ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd, Anh \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Tunisia c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 1-1 v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 10 k\u00e9m t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1, \u1edf 2 tr\u1eadn xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n 3 b\u00e0n l\u00e0 Ph\u00e1p 2-1 Australia v\u00e0 B\u1ec9 3-0 Panama, nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 3 c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ebfn ho\u1eb7c ph\u00fat 75 ho\u1eb7c 80. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u1ee9ng minh r\u1eb1ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e1c xa qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn c\u1ee7a h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tham d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ng\u00e2y th\u01a1 nh\u01b0 x\u01b0a.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi tuyen Senegal tai World Cup 2018\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Senegal t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/8/dt-senegal-tai-world-cup-2018-hy-vong-vao-ky-tich.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Senegal t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1edbn</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Senegal vs Ba Lan kh\u00f4ng d\u00e1m \u0111i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i quy lu\u1eadt \u0111\u00f3. Nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ecbu tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m ra th\u1eed th\u00e1ch cho d\u00e2n d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 d\u00e1m \u0111\u1eb7t c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c t\u1ed5ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u00e0 2. Theo h\u1ecd suy ngh\u0129, v\u1edbi hai \u0111\u1ed9i Senegal v\u00e0 Ba Lan, 2 l\u01b0\u1edbi rung n\u1ebfu xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u0169ng l\u00e0 xa x\u1ec9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSenegal \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n cho ch\u00e2u Phi tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018, nh\u01b0ng 22/23 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. Ngo\u1ea1i l\u1ec7 duy nh\u1ea5t t\u1edbi t\u1eeb th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Khadim N'Diaye khi \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Horoya c\u1ee7a Guinea. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Senegal \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5m nhu\u1ea7n t\u01b0 t\u01b0\u1edfng khoa h\u1ecdc, k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt v\u00e0 ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng \u1edf b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ecba gi\u00e0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/dt-senegal-tai-world-cup-2018-hy-vong-vao-ky-tich-469-188074.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/8/dt-senegal-tai-world-cup-2018-hy-vong-vao-ky-tich.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/dt-senegal-tai-world-cup-2018-hy-vong-vao-ky-tich-469-188074.html\">\u0110T Senegal t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018: Hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o k\u1ef3 t\u00edch</span><br>\r\n<span>D\u00f9 n\u1eb1m trong b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 ngang t\u00e0i ngang s\u1ee9c, nh\u01b0ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Senegal b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin chung v\u1ec1 \u0110T Senegal t\u1ea1i World...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi ta ch\u00fa \u00fd nhi\u1ec1u t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Senegal c\u00f3 c\u00e1c m\u0169i c\u00f4ng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0 Sadio Man\u00e9, Mame Biram Diouf, M'Baye Niang, Keita Bald\u00e9, Diafra Sakho&hellip; Tuy nhi\u00ean, ph\u00f2ng tuy\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 t\u1ea7m th\u01b0\u1eddng. Kalidou Koulibaly (Napoli) r\u1ed3i Cheikhou Kouyate, Idrissa Gueye, Alfred N'Diaye, Badou Ndiaye ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i Anh tr\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec1u \u1edf 3 tuy\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 v\u1eefng v\u00e0ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n10 tr\u1eadn c\u1ea3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u00e0 giao h\u1eefu v\u1eeba qua, Senegal ch\u1ec9 l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u00f3 6 b\u00e0n bao g\u1ed3m 4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Burkina Faso, Croatia. Trong \u0111\u00f3, &ldquo;S\u01b0 t\u1eed v\u00f9ng Teranga&rdquo; c\u0169ng c\u00f3 6 l\u1ea7n gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch m\u00e0nh l\u01b0\u1edbi. H\u1ecd l\u00e0 t\u00e1c nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh khi\u1ebfn 10 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 7 l\u00e0 2 b\u00e0n tr\u1edf xu\u1ed1ng. T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1, nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Senegal vs Ba Lan c\u0169ng nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kalidou Koulibaly\" title=\"Kalidou Koulibaly\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/8/19/Diem-tin-Bong-da-toi-ngay-212-MU-hoi-mua-tien-ve-cua-Barca-hinh-anh-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Koulibaly l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u Phi</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nBa Lan c\u00f3 ch\u1ee7 c\u00f4ng Robert Lewandowski xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed. T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 khu v\u1ef1c ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, Lewy \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 16 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng sau 10 tr\u1eadn, h\u01a1n b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 Cristiano Ronaldo (15 b\u00e0n). Nh\u01b0ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u00e0 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Ba Lan khi \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00e1 d\u1ec5 th\u1edf v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng Montenegro, Romania, Armenia, Kazakhstan&hellip; \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 &ldquo;m\u1ed3i ngon&rdquo;. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Ba Lan r\u1ea5t gi\u1ed1ng v\u1edbi Euro 2016. H\u1ecd v\u00e0 Lewandowski c\u0169ng n\u00e3 v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ec3u r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1edbi VCK \u0111\u1ea7y v\u1ebb vang. Nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t m\u1eb7t c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5t Ph\u00e1p kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n, m\u1ed9t m\u1eb7t thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i, &ldquo;\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng tr\u1eafng&rdquo; th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lewandowski Ba Lan tai World Cup 2018\" title=\"Lewandowski Ba Lan t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/7/lewand.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ba Lan ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o ch\u1ee7 c\u00f4ng Lewandowski</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n5 tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1ecb B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha lo\u1ea1i \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, Ba Lan ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f3 4 b\u00e0n, t\u1ee9c trung b\u00ecnh ch\u01b0a t\u1edbi 1 b\u00e0n/ tr\u1eadn. C\u0169ng \u0111\u1eebng qu\u00ean r\u1eb1ng 3 trong s\u1ed1 6 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu n\u1eeda n\u0103m qua, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 3 kh\u00f4ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 b\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ea3m cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi s\u1ebd khan hi\u1ebfm b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. C\u00e1c fan b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb9p c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch, nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c fan \u0111am m\u00ea d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ni\u1ec1m vui l\u1edbn. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Ch\u1ecdn:</strong> \u00cdt b\u00e0n th\u1eafng (t\u1eeb 2 tr\u1edf xu\u1ed1ng)<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea quan tr\u1ecdng:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n- 9/14 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018 c\u00f3 t\u1eeb 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u1edf xu\u1ed1ng.<br>\r\n- Senegal ch\u1ec9 l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi 6 b\u00e0n sau 10 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n- Senegal gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi \u1edf 6 trong s\u1ed1 10 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n- 7/10 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Senegal kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 2 b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n- Ba Lan ch\u1ec9 ghi 4 b\u00e0n sau 5 tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i Euro 2016.<br>\r\n- Ba Lan &ldquo;t\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i&rdquo; 3 trong s\u1ed1 6 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ch\u00ednh:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n- <strong>\u00cdt b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</strong> (t\u1eeb 2 tr\u1edf xu\u1ed1ng)<br>\r\n<strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3:</strong> Ba Lan th\u1eafng 1-0 ho\u1eb7c h\u00f2a 0-0<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t kh\u00e1c:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n- S\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 1 trong 2 \u0111\u1ed9i ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n- T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 10 (U 9 1/2).<br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c hi\u1ec7p 1 c\u1ee7a Ba Lan nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n (-1/2).<br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a Ba Lan nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n (-1).<br>\r\n- T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 3 (O 3).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-nhat-ban-vs-colombia-va-du-doan-nhat-ban-vs-colombia-421-188919.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/tuong-thuat-colombia-vs-nhat-ban.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-nhat-ban-vs-colombia-va-du-doan-nhat-ban-vs-colombia-421-188919.html\">Nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n v\u00e0ng cho tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u gi\u1edd \u0111\u1eb9p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n vs Colombia</span><br>\r\n<span>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n vs Colombia v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. Nh\u01b0ng h\u00e3y c\u00f9ng Bongda24h.vn b\u00f3c tr\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt \u1edf sau c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9...</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/tuong-thuat-colombia-vs-nhat-ban-463-188923.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/tuong-thuat-colombia-vs-nhat-ban.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/tuong-thuat-colombia-vs-nhat-ban-463-188923.html\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Colombia vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n 19h00 ng\u00e0y 19/6 (World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\n<span>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Colombia vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 xem tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Colombia vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n b\u1ea3ng H World Cup 2018 l\u00fac...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ea3i Ly (TTVN)<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"354","checkdouble":"188933"},{"date":"16:37 19/06","title":"Liverpool ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Sturridge v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 b\u00e8o","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/26/liverpool-chot-gia-ban-sturridge-voi-gia-beo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Kane. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 47 tu\u1ed5i d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen cho ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Tottenham song c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean \u201cxo\u00e1y nh\u1eb9\u201d v\u00e0o n\u1ed7i \u0111au l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a anh.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kane t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u00ean \u0110T Anh</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018, HLV Gareth Southgate quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh trao b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Anh cho Harry Kane. \u0110\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, nghe \u0111\u00e2u chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia 47 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i g\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec7n cho Jordan Henderson v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Liverpool tham d\u1ef1 chung k\u1ebft Champions League v\u1edbi Real Madrid.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede \u0111\u00f3, Southgate \u0111\u00e3 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o v\u00e0 tr\u1ea5n an Henderson sau khi ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ea1i b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng cho Kane. R\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea7y c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin l\u1edbn, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 24 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb \u00e1p l\u1ef1c m\u00e0 c\u00f2n t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Kane sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Tunisia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Kane sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Tunisia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/hlv-southgate-phat-bieu-ve-kane.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Kane l\u1eadp c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Tunisia gi\u00fap Anh th\u1eafng 2-1</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Tunisia \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3ng G VCK World Cup 2018, ch\u00ednh Kane \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap gi\u00fap \u0110T Anh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1. \u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd, b\u00e0n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a trung phong s\u1ed1 9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi \u1edf ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean khi Tam s\u01b0 t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i chia \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c Southgate h\u1ebft l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ea1i Euro 2016, Kane \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o. Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, HLV Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Kane v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen. Nh\u01b0ng b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Anh c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean \u201cch\u1ecdc qu\u00ea\u201d h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c \u201ct\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i\u201d su\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 8 t\u1ea1i CLB.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gareth Southgate phat bieu ve tran Anh vs Tunisia\" title=\"Gareth Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Anh vs Tunisia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/gareth-southgate-ngoai-kane-cac-chan-sut-con-lai-cua-anh-qua-toi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Kane v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi khen</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cN\u1ebfu Harry Kane kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi c\u00e1c c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y\u201d, Southgate n\u00f3i. \u201c\u0110i\u1ec1u duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01b0a l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 8. C\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, Kane \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 m\u1ecdi r\u00e0o c\u1ea3n kh\u00e1c v\u00e0 t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i bi\u1ebft Kane \u0111ang c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o khi l\u0129nh x\u01b0\u1edbng \u0110TQG c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a World Cup. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n19h ng\u00e0y ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt t\u1edbi, Anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Panama t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Nizhny Novgorod. M\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap h\u1ecd g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u00f3 v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i\u00a0 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem l\u1ea1i video Kane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Tunisia:</strong>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/19/kane.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-tunisia-12-anh-harry-kane-xung-danh-doi-truong-421-188886.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/du-am-tunisia-12-anh-harry-kane-xung-danh-doi-truong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-tunisia-12-anh-harry-kane-xung-danh-doi-truong-421-188886.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Tunisia 1-2 Anh: Harry Kane! X\u1ee9ng danh \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng</span><br>\r\n<span>Harry Kane t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap gi\u00fap Anh \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Tunisia 2-1 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018, ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng minh t\u1ea1i sao anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c...</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/lap-cu-dup-cuu-roi-tam-su-harry-kane-phan-khich-cuc-do-421-188883.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/DT-Anh-gianh-chien-thang-truoc-Tunisia-Hy-vong-tu-2-chang-Harry-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/lap-cu-dup-cuu-roi-tam-su-harry-kane-phan-khich-cuc-do-421-188883.html\">L\u1eadp c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap c\u1ee9u r\u1ed7i Tam S\u01b0, Harry Kane ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ed9</span><br>\r\n<span>2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Tam S\u01b0 c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n. Sau tr\u1eadn, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Harry Kane chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng Tunisia.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"353","checkdouble":"188935"},{"date":"16:56 19/06","title":"\u0110\u00e2y! B\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Wilshere n\u1ebfu r\u1eddi Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/18/day-ben-do-moi-cua-wilshere-neu-roi-arsenal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Jack Wilshere t\u1edbi Southampton \u0111ang l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n St Mary \u0111ang l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Jack Wilshere v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 7 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jack Wilshere v\u1edbi Arsenal s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n. \u0110\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a quy\u1ebft\u00a0\u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh hay kh\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jack Wilshere t\u1edbi Southampton theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Jack Wilshere t\u1edbi Southampton theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/18/day-ben-do-moi-cua-wilshere-neu-roi-arsenal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Wilshere v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft s\u1ebd ra \u0111i hay \u1edf l\u1ea1i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Daily Mail, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi. Theo \u0111\u00f3, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/wilshere-se-chot-tuong-lai-sau-cuoc-gap-hlv-emery-172-188179.html\" target=\"_blank\">Wilshere s\u1ebd n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi Emery \u0111\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</span>.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Emery \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Ramsey v\u00e0 Xhaka, b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 2 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Arsenal. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Lucas Torreira v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 26.4 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Jack Wilshere s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, anh s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0o s\u00e2n t\u1eeb b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n v\u00e0 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Southampton \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Jack Wilshere</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Jack Wilshere t\u1edbi Southampton \u0111ang l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n St Mary \u0111ang l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Wilshere tran Arsenal vs Atletico\" title=\"Wilshere tran Arsenal vs Atletico\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/27/Gareth-Southgate-phat-bieu-ve-Jack-Wilshere-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Southampton mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Wilshere\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMirror kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Southampton \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng cho ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n St Mary c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 100.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Wilshere d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 c\u0169ng \u01b0ng v\u1edbi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0y, n\u1ebfu chia tay Arsenal nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng anh s\u1ebd c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Southampton. Ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n St Mary th\u00ec nh\u1eefng West Ham, Wolves, Sampdoria v\u00e0 AC Milan c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u1ea3i th\u1ea3m \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00f3n ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y khi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, khi \u0111\u00f3 Southampton, West Ham v\u00e0 Wolves s\u1ebd c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf trong vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Arsenal.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"352","checkdouble":"188936"},{"date":"16:33 19/06","title":"4 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 Argentina c\u1ea7n s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/4-van-de-argentina-can-sua-chua-ngay-lap-tuc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Argentina \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland. \u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00e1i l\u1eadp th\u00e0nh t\u00edch l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft nh\u01b0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 4 n\u0103m, Argentina c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i thay \u0111\u1ed5i v\u00e0 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n.</h2><h2>S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 kh\u00e1c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Sampaoli m\u1edbi hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1i sao khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, Argentina l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 Javier Mascherano v\u00e0 Lucas Biglia xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mascherano t\u1eebng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi c\u1ea3 th\u1ee7 l\u1eabn c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00e2n ma thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a anh gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebfn m\u1ea5t. Biglia th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n. Ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a AC Milan \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t \u0111i kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 r\u00ea d\u1eaft b\u00f3ng th\u1eddi c\u00f2n tr\u1ebb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"4 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 Argentina c\u1ea7n s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"4 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 Argentina c\u1ea7n s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/4-van-de-Argentina-can-sua-chua-ngay-lap-tuc-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sampaoli m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m khi b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Iceland</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Messi ph\u1ea3i l\u00f9i s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ec3 tri\u1ec3n khai b\u00f3ng. V\u00e0 nh\u1edd v\u1eady, h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Iceland c\u00e0ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o h\u01a1n khi Messi kh\u00f4ng \u1edf g\u1ea7n khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111e d\u1ecda ghi b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ever Banega l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 duy nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Argentina c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng l\u00ean tuy\u1ebfn tr\u00ean ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o v\u00e0 gi\u1ecfi ph\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. Nh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u00fat 54, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tung v\u00e0o s\u00e2n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, Argentina s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Croatia. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u c\u00f3 h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n Iceland nhi\u1ec1u. V\u00e0 Banega s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t. Ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Sevilla c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean duy nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng anh h\u00e0o \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Croatia nh\u01b0 Luka Modric, Ivan Rakitic hay Mateo Kovacic.</div>\r\n<h2>Lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 HLV Sampaoli \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf c\u1ea5p CLB. Di Maria ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean l\u00e0m n\u00f3ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf PSG. Biglia v\u00e0 Marcos Rojo c\u0169ng d\u00e0nh h\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 c\u1ea3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua \u0111\u1ec3 xem c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Di Maria\" title=\"Di Maria\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/162727-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Di Maria g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ra qu\u00e2n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mascherano bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Trung Qu\u1ed1c do qu\u00e1 sa s\u00fat. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Eduardo Salvio \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh \u1edf Benfica nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i ph\u1ea3i cam ch\u1ecbu ch\u01a1i h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean khi\u1ebfn cho th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 sung m\u00e3n. V\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ed3n \u00e9p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Argentina.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia s\u1eafp t\u1edbi, HLV Sampaoli c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng ngu\u1ed3n n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u01b0\u01a1i m\u1edbi m\u00e0 m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 thay v\u00ec c\u1ee9 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i ng\u00f4i sao. Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, Cristian Pavon \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n trong 15 ph\u00fat ra s\u00e2n so v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a Di Maria.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 Pavon, Federico Fazio hay Gabriel Mercado x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t thay v\u00ec nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00e1c trong \u0111\u1ed9i. Sampaoli c\u1ea7n t\u1edbi ngu\u1ed3n n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 mu\u1ed1n gi\u00fap Argentina v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua b\u1ea3ng t\u1eed th\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u00f4ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Willy Caballero</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1edb ra l\u1ea7n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng Argentina c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh l\u00e0 khi n\u00e0o. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t ra v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eddi HLV Argentina.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Argentina l\u00e0 Sergio Romero \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc World Cup. Nh\u01b0ng ngay c\u1ea3 Romero c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Willy Caballero\" title=\"Willy Caballero\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/162640-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Willy Caballero c\u00f3 m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i trong b\u00e0n thua c\u1ee7a Argentina tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch m\u00e0 HLV Sampaoli b\u1ecf qua m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0111ang l\u00ean nh\u01b0 Geronimo Rulli c\u1ee7a Real Sociedad. Tuy nhi\u00ean, n\u1ebfu Sampaoli mu\u1ed1n Argentina ti\u1ebfn xa, trao su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh cho Caballero l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i k\u1ecb.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Caballero r\u1ea5t k\u00e9m. Anh th\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng khai t\u00e1c t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh hay ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c. Ngay c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Caballero c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn cho \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y lo l\u1eafng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nahuel Guzman v\u00e0 Franco Armani l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n kh\u00e1c trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. C\u1ea3 hai th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u (c\u00f9ng 32 tu\u1ed5i). Tuy kh\u00f4ng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0 Caballero nh\u01b0ng hai th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u1edf c\u1ea5p CLB. V\u00e0 \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo, Sampaoli n\u00ean th\u1eed trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n kh\u00e1c thay v\u00ec Caballero.</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1ea9y Messi l\u00ean h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Messi l\u00e0 l\u00fd do duy nh\u1ea5t gi\u00fap Argentina tham d\u1ef1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00f2ng chung k\u1ebft <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span>. V\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh La Albiceleste n\u0103m nay s\u1ebd \u0111i xa t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n Messi. V\u00e0 khi nh\u1eefng k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea1t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Argentina th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e2m v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng b\u1ebf t\u1eafc to\u00e0n t\u1eadp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Messi Argentina 1-1 Iceland\" title=\"Messi Argentina 1-1 Iceland\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/maradona-bao-ve-messi-chi-trich-nhan-to-khac-cua-argentina.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Messi c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ra qu\u00e2n th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Iceland \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t khi theo s\u00e1t t\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc di chuy\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a Messi. V\u00e0 M10 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 th\u1ee9 ma thu\u1eadt n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi m\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 k\u00e9m c\u1ecfi, Messi c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n l\u00e0 bao. Anh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ph\u1ea3i l\u00f9i s\u00e2u v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Iceland \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sampaoli s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed Messi \u0111\u00e1 g\u1ea7n v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. V\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00e1c n\u00e0y, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u00f9i l\u1ea1i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Albiceleste c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 chuy\u1ec3n tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i nhanh h\u01a1n. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 m\u00e0 Banega v\u00e0 Lo Celso c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3. C\u1ea3 hai c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u00e0y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Argentina hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"351","checkdouble":"188938"},{"date":"17:09 19/06","title":"HLV \u0110T Anh ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i \u201cv\u1eeba \u0111\u1ea5m, v\u1eeba xoa\u201d v\u1edbi Kane","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/hlv-southgate-phat-bieu-ve-kane.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Kane. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 47 tu\u1ed5i d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen cho ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Tottenham song c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean \u201cxo\u00e1y nh\u1eb9\u201d v\u00e0o n\u1ed7i \u0111au l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a anh.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kane t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u00ean \u0110T Anh</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018, HLV Gareth Southgate quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh trao b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Anh cho Harry Kane. \u0110\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, nghe \u0111\u00e2u chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia 47 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i g\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec7n cho Jordan Henderson v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Liverpool tham d\u1ef1 chung k\u1ebft Champions League v\u1edbi Real Madrid.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede \u0111\u00f3, Southgate \u0111\u00e3 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o v\u00e0 tr\u1ea5n an Henderson sau khi ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ea1i b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng cho Kane. R\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea7y c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin l\u1edbn, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 24 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb \u00e1p l\u1ef1c m\u00e0 c\u00f2n t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Kane sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Tunisia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Kane sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Tunisia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/hlv-southgate-phat-bieu-ve-kane.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Kane l\u1eadp c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Tunisia gi\u00fap Anh th\u1eafng 2-1</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Tunisia \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3ng G VCK World Cup 2018, ch\u00ednh Kane \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap gi\u00fap \u0110T Anh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1. \u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd, b\u00e0n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a trung phong s\u1ed1 9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi \u1edf ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean khi Tam s\u01b0 t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i chia \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c Southgate h\u1ebft l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ea1i Euro 2016, Kane \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o. Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, HLV Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Kane v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen. Nh\u01b0ng b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Anh c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean \u201cch\u1ecdc qu\u00ea\u201d h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c \u201ct\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i\u201d su\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 8 t\u1ea1i CLB.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gareth Southgate phat bieu ve tran Anh vs Tunisia\" title=\"Gareth Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Anh vs Tunisia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/gareth-southgate-ngoai-kane-cac-chan-sut-con-lai-cua-anh-qua-toi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Kane v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi khen</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cN\u1ebfu Harry Kane kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi c\u00e1c c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y\u201d, Southgate n\u00f3i. \u201c\u0110i\u1ec1u duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01b0a l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 8. C\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, Kane \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 m\u1ecdi r\u00e0o c\u1ea3n kh\u00e1c v\u00e0 t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i bi\u1ebft Kane \u0111ang c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o khi l\u0129nh x\u01b0\u1edbng \u0110TQG c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a World Cup. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n19h ng\u00e0y ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt t\u1edbi, Anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Panama t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Nizhny Novgorod. M\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap h\u1ecd g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u00f3 v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i\u00a0 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem l\u1ea1i video Kane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Tunisia:</strong>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/19/kane.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-tunisia-12-anh-harry-kane-xung-danh-doi-truong-421-188886.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/du-am-tunisia-12-anh-harry-kane-xung-danh-doi-truong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-tunisia-12-anh-harry-kane-xung-danh-doi-truong-421-188886.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Tunisia 1-2 Anh: Harry Kane! X\u1ee9ng danh \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng</span><br>\r\n<span>Harry Kane t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap gi\u00fap Anh \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Tunisia 2-1 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018, ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng minh t\u1ea1i sao anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c...</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/lap-cu-dup-cuu-roi-tam-su-harry-kane-phan-khich-cuc-do-421-188883.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/DT-Anh-gianh-chien-thang-truoc-Tunisia-Hy-vong-tu-2-chang-Harry-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/lap-cu-dup-cuu-roi-tam-su-harry-kane-phan-khich-cuc-do-421-188883.html\">L\u1eadp c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap c\u1ee9u r\u1ed7i Tam S\u01b0, Harry Kane ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ed9</span><br>\r\n<span>2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Tam S\u01b0 c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n. Sau tr\u1eadn, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Harry Kane chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng Tunisia.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"350","checkdouble":"188939"},{"date":"17:05 19/06","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Ba Lan vs Senegal 22h00 ng\u00e0y 19/6 (World Cup 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/tuong-thuat-ba-lan-vs-senegal.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Ba Lan vs Senegal: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 xem tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ba Lan vs Senegal b\u1ea3ng H World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 22h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 19/6.</h2><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Ba Lan vs Senegal: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 xem tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ba Lan vs Senegal b\u1ea3ng H World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 22h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 19/6.</h2>\r\nKh\u00f4ng xem \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, vui l\u00f2ng click v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e2y <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/tuong-thuat-ba-lan-vs-senegal-463-188940.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\"><u><strong>TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP BA LAN VS SENEGAL</strong></u></span></span><br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"349","checkdouble":"188940"},{"date":"17:08 19/06","title":"Anh h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Tunisia, m\u1ed9t C\u0110V\u2026 nh\u1ea3y l\u00ean n\u1eafp capo \u0103n m\u1eebng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/anh-ha-guc-tunisia-mot-cdv-nhay-len-nap-capo-an-mung.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Song song v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c si\u00eau sao t\u1ea1i VCK World Cup 2018, c\u00e1c kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 tr\u00ean kh\u1eafp th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi c\u0169ng lu\u00f4n bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch \u0103n m\u1eebng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, m\u1ed9t C\u0110V Anh nh\u1ea3y l\u00ean n\u1eafp capo, sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Harry Kane v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nHooligan \u0103n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba k\u1ebft th\u00fac r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng nay, nh\u1eefng ch\u00fa s\u01b0 t\u1eed n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Tunisia v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1, trong \u0111\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Harry Kane ghi c\u1ea3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. \u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd, pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi \u1edf ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do c\u1ea3 n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0103n m\u1eebng cu\u1ed3ng nhi\u1ec7t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00ean The Sun, m\u1ed9t \u0111o\u1ea1n video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p m\u00e0n \u0103n m\u1eebng c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 tr\u00ean kh\u1eafp x\u1ee9 s\u1edf s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9, t\u1eeb London \u0111\u1ebfn Manchester. Trong \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t C\u0110V Anh nh\u1ea3y l\u00ean n\u1eafp capo v\u00ec qu\u00e1 sung s\u01b0\u1edbng. H\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111i\u00ean r\u1ed3 n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 x\u1ea3y ra tai n\u1ea1n, nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 anh ch\u00e0ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 h\u1ea5n g\u00ec.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1eafng Tunisia, C\u0110V Anh \u0103n m\u1eebng b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch nh\u1ea3y l\u00ean n\u1eafp \u00f4 t\u00f4 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1eafng Tunisia, C\u0110V Anh \u0103n m\u1eebng b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch nh\u1ea3y l\u00ean n\u1eafp \u00f4 t\u00f4 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/eng.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh C\u0110V Anh \u0103n m\u1eebng b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch nh\u1ea3y l\u00ean n\u1eafp \u00f4 t\u00f4</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111ang chinh chi\u1ebfn tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd h\u1ecd c\u0169ng &ldquo;h\u1ed1t ho\u1ea3ng&rdquo; n\u1ebfu ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n \u0103n m\u1eebng qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/thang-hoanh-trang-nguoi-dan-nga-mang-gau-ra-duong-an-mung-421-188561.html\" target=\"_blank\">c\u00e1c C\u0110V Nga \u0111\u00e3... mang c\u1ea3 g\u1ea5u ra \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng</span> sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Saudi Arabia. M\u1eebng World Cup l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t, nh\u01b0ng vui th\u00f4i ch\u1ee9 \u0111\u1eebng vui qu\u00e1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0103n m\u1eebng c\u1ee7a hooligan Anh sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tunisia<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/19/england.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\">\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/19/england~1.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; backg