alt=\"Toni Kross\" title=\"Toni Kross\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/5_1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Toni Kross \"b\u00e9o quay\" kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi v\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p trai l\u00e3ng t\u1eed th\u01b0\u1eddng ng\u00e0y.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mohamed Salah\" title=\"Mohamed Salah\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/174812-4.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Mohamed Salah, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Ai C\u1eadp nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ra s\u00e2n v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng vai.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"De Gea\" title=\"De Gea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/3_1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">De Gea tr\u00f4ng th\u1eadt l\u1ea1nh l\u00f9ng d\u00f9 b\u1ecb ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \"n\u00e9m \u0111\u00e1\" kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng ngh\u1ec9 v\u00ec nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cristiano Ronaldo\" title=\"Cristiano Ronaldo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/2_1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Cristiano Ronaldo lu\u00f4n gi\u1eef v\u1ebb m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1eafc th\u1eafng, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 sau khi gi\u00e0nh c\u00fa hat-trick ngay trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lionel Messi\" title=\"Lionel Messi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/1_1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Lionel Messi trong b\u1ed9 d\u1ea1ng kh\u1eafc kh\u1ed5 ch\u1eafc v\u00ec s\u00fat h\u1ecfng penalty khi g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \"h\u1ea1t ti\u00eau\" Iceland.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"346","checkdouble":"188944"},{"date":"09:10 19/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nga vs Ai C\u1eadp (1h00 ng\u00e0y 20/6): Salah, Salah v\u00e0... Salah","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/Nhan-dinh-Nga-vs-Ai-Cap-(1h00-ngay-206)-Salah,-Salah-va-Salah-hinh-anh-2.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Salah, Salah v\u00e0 Salah, nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi t\u1ea7n su\u1ea5t l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1eefa Nga vs Ai C\u1eadp v\u1eabn ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 Mohamed Salah.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Nga vs Ai C\u1eadp, ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn c\u00e1c t\u1edd b\u00e1o \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1eadp t\u1edbi Mohamed Salah. C\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i th\u00f4i, Salah \u0111ang l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ai C\u1eadp. \u1ede v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 ba World Cup 2018 khu v\u1ef1c ch\u00e2u Phi, Salah ghi \u0111\u1ebfn 5 trong s\u1ed1 8 b\u00e0n, gi\u00fap \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111\u1ebfn Nga h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nga vs Ai C\u1eadp (1h00 ng\u00e0y 206) Salah, Salah v\u00e0 Salah h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nga vs Ai C\u1eadp (1h00 ng\u00e0y 206) Salah, Salah v\u00e0 Salah h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/salah-11.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Mohamed Salah l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Nga vs Ai C\u1eadp.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ai C\u1eadp tin r\u1eb1ng n\u1ebfu Salah xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Uruguay, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u00edt nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu c\u1ea3nh tr\u1eafng tay.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Hector Cuper kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Salah tr\u0103m ph\u1ea7n tr\u0103m s\u1ebd ra s\u00e2n tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, d\u00f9 r\u1eb1ng gi\u1edbi ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean ch\u1ee5p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3nh anh ph\u1ea3i nh\u1edd s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eb7c \u00e1o t\u1eadp. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f2n c\u00e1ch n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c, \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp \u0111ang r\u01a1i v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf r\u1ea5t b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Saudi Arabia v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 5-0, trong khi Ai C\u1eadp thua Uruguay. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn \u0110T Nga c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i \u0111\u01b0a ra nhi\u1ec1u toan t\u00ednh h\u01a1n b\u1edfi ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m trong hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Ai C\u1eadp bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n t\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft b\u1edfi ngay c\u1ea3 khi c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a, h\u1ecd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng th\u1eadt \u0111\u1eadm Saudi Arabia r\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ee3i Uruguay h\u1ea1 Nga \u1edf lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. C\u00f2n n\u1ebfu th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda World Cup 2018 s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1eebng \u0111\u00f9a v\u1edbi Nga<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 c\u00f3 Mohamed Salah nh\u01b0ng \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nga tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Krestovsky. H\u1ecd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, trong khi Nga ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m v\u1edbi Saudi Arabia.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nga vs Ai C\u1eadp (1h00 ng\u00e0y 206) Salah, Salah v\u00e0 Salah h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nga vs Ai C\u1eadp (1h00 ng\u00e0y 206) Salah, Salah v\u00e0 Salah h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/Nhan-dinh-Nga-vs-Ai-Cap-(1h00-ngay-206)-Salah,-Salah-va-Salah-hinh-anh-2.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Nga vs Ai C\u1eadp mang t\u00ednh quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u1edbn v\u1edbi su\u1ea5t \u0111i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng A World Cup 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSaudi Arabia qu\u00e1 ng\u00e2y th\u01a1 khi ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Nga nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn l\u00e0 HLV Stanislav Cherchesov \u0111\u00e3 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. V\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc cu\u1ed9c g\u1eb7p Ai C\u1eadp, HLV Cherchesov t\u1ef1 tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn Mohamed Salah ph\u1ea3i im ti\u1ebfng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Nga v\u1eabn c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 Dzyuba, Smolov, Golovin hay Cheryshev - c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Villareal, ng\u01b0\u1eddi hi\u1ebfm hoi thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i trong \u0110T Nga l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Cherchesov nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng, sau \u0111\u00f3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng pha b\u00f3ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n. Dzyuba ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd k\u1ef9 nh\u1ea5t trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng, b\u1edfi \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o cao \u0111\u1ebfn 1m96 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 trung t\u00e2m b\u00f3ng h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Th\u00f4ng tin l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng:</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Nga:</strong> Dzagoev kh\u00f4ng ra s\u00e2n v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Ai C\u1eadp:</strong> T\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe c\u1ee7a Salah v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u1ea9n s\u1ed1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn:</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean hai \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n g\u1eb7p nhau.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a Li\u00ean X\u00f4, Nga ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng thua c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u Phi t\u1ea1i World Cup (th\u1eafng 2, h\u00f2a 1), bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 6-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Cameroon n\u0103m 1994, v\u1edbi Oleg Salenko ghi c\u1ea3 5 b\u00e0n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* Ai C\u1eadp ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u \u00c2u t\u1ea1i World Cup (h\u00f2a 2, thua 2).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi Li\u00ean X\u00f4 tan r\u00e3, Nga ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng \u1edf 3 k\u1ef3 World Cup \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham d\u1ef1 (1994, 2002 v\u00e0 2014).&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* S\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0110T Nga ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 (5) nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n hai k\u1ef3 World Cup g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t h\u1ecd g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t l\u00e0 2014 (2) v\u00e0 2002 (4).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Nga vs Ai C\u1eadp (1h00 ng\u00e0y 20/6):</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Nga (4-2-3-1):</strong> 1.Akinfeev - 2.M.Fernandes, 3.Kutepov, 4.Ignashevich, 18.Zhirkov - 8.Gazinskiy, 11.Zobnin - 19.Samedov, 17.Golovin, 6.Cheryshev - 10.Smolov</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Ai C\u1eadp (4-2-3-1):</strong> 23.El-Shenawy - 7.Fathy, 2.Gabr, 6.Hegazi, 13.Shafy - 8.Hamed, 17.Elneny - 10.Salah, 19.Said, 21.Trezeguet - 9.Mohsen</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1:</strong> Nga 2-2 Ai C\u1eadp<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Nga vs Ai Cap\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Nga vs Ai C\u1eadp\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/Nga-vs-Ai-Cap-(4-2-3-1-vs-4-2-3-1).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Nga vs Ai C\u1eadp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong> </strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Nh\u01b0 \u0110\u1ea1t (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"345","checkdouble":"188902"},{"date":"09:56 19/06","title":"Man City ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d 46,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/26/man-city-sap-co-jorginho-cua-napoli.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Man City s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Jorginho c\u1ee7a Napoli. Theo ngu\u1ed3n tin c\u1ee7a Sky Sports, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chi 46,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Man City li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Jorginho l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u1eeb l\u00e2u. \u0110\u1ebfn l\u00fac n\u00e0y, ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u00fd k\u1ebft. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111ang ch\u1edd 2 CLB \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed3ng thu\u1eadn, bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh thanh to\u00e1n, ph\u1ee5 ph\u00ed v\u00e0 l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu c\u1ee7a \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng chi ti\u1ebft nh\u1ecf v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i Man City s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Jorginho.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Man City s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Jorginho c\u1ee7a Napoli gi\u00e1 46,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Man City s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Jorginho c\u1ee7a Napoli gi\u00e1 46,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/26/man-city-sap-co-jorginho-cua-napoli.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Man City s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Jorginho c\u1ee7a Napoli gi\u00e1 46,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nJorginho m\u1edbi \u0111\u0103ng m\u1ed9t t\u1ea5m \u1ea3nh tr\u00ean Instagram v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 c\u00f9ng gia \u0111\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i Brazil. Anh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd bay t\u1edbi Manchester ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf khi n\u00e0o 2 CLB th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Jorginho \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 37 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho Napoli m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng bao g\u1ed3m 1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00ednh Man City t\u1ea1i Champions League h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 11.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nJorginho b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i Verona tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Napoli n\u0103m 2014. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i nhanh ch\u00f3ng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. K\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u00f9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111i\u1ec1u ph\u1ed1i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Jorginho gi\u00fap l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Napoli th\u00eam ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m m\u1ea1i v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMan City c\u1ee7a HLV Pep Guardiola c\u0169ng ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Yaya Toure m\u1edbi ra \u0111i sau khi h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng, h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf v\u00e0 Jorginho l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o. Guardiola r\u1ea5t th\u00edch phong c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Italia v\u00e0 tin anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Man City tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/soc-raheem-sterling-tu-choi-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-man-city-172-188324.html\">S\u1ed1c: Raheem Sterling t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Man City</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/doi-bong-dau-tien-dam-phan-voi-yaya-toure-172-188052.html\">\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Yaya Toure</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/neymar-tha-thinh-man-city-pep-van-rat-tinh-don-172-187954.html\">Neymar \u201cth\u1ea3 th\u00ednh\u201d Man City, Pep v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t t\u1ec9nh \u0111\u00f2n</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"344","checkdouble":"188904"},{"date":"10:42 19/06","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Fekir l\u1ea1i m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/29/nguoi-dai-dien-cua-fekir-lai-moi-goi-liverpool.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>CSKA t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Golovin cho Juventus. D\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 17 tri\u1ec7u Euro nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ea1i gia Italia v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang n\u1ed5i \u0111\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e1m t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Golovin t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga khan hi\u1ebfm nh\u00e2n t\u00e0i, Aleksandr Golovin n\u1ed5i l\u00ean nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng. \u1ede tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, \u201cNh\u1eefng ch\u00fa g\u1ea5u\u201d \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ho\u00e0nh tr\u00e1ng 5-0. \u1ede \u0111\u00f3, d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t r\u00f5 n\u00e9t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGolovin \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 2 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho Nga t\u1eeb qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c v\u00e0 cho th\u1ea5y \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf CSKA Moscow. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, t\u1eeb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18, \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CSKA t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Golovin cho Juventus gi\u00e1 17 tri\u1ec7u Euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CSKA t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Golovin cho Juventus gi\u00e1 17 tri\u1ec7u Euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/cska-tu-choi-ban-golovin-cho-juventus.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Golovin t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o tuy\u1ec3n Nga</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n27 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho CSKA t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Nga, Golovin c\u00f3 5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 1 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. \u1ede c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996 h\u1ed9i t\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ee7 nh\u1eefng t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00f4ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng, ki\u1ebfn thi\u1ebft, \u0111i b\u00f3ng cho t\u1edbi s\u00fat xa.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Juventus mu\u1ed1n Golovin nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea5t th\u00e0nh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgay sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Golovin t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng gi\u00fap Nga th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u vang d\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Juventus t\u1eeb suy ngh\u0129 mang anh v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng. H\u1ecd g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 17 tri\u1ec7u Euro t\u1edbi CSKA \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1eaft x\u00edch m\u00ecnh mu\u1ed1n b\u1ed5 sung.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Aleksandr Golovin\" title=\"tien ve Aleksandr Golovin\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/4/Juventus-muon-mua-Aleksandr-Golovin-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">CSKA t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Golovin cho Juventus</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTi\u1ebfc r\u1eb1ng l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c CSKA t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Golovin cho Juventus. M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 thu v\u1ec1 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 25 tri\u1ec7u Euro sau th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i v\u1ed9i v\u00e0ng khi c\u00f3 kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u li\u00ean h\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Golovin. M\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u00e1 gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c b\u00ean s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn CSKA \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f2n Juventus, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00e2u s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa. \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u01a1 b\u1eafp nh\u01b0 Sami Khedira, Blaise Matuidi hay Stefano Sturaro, Bianconeri mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u00eam ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 Miralem Pjanic trong kh\u00e2u s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o, \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u1ecd tin c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Rodrigo Bentancur ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Aleksandr Golovin tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhm-arsenal-nhan-hlv-unai-emery-hay-ngay-lap-tuc-mua-golovin-172-188557.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/nhm-arsenal-nhan-hlv-unai-emery-hay-ngay-lap-tuc-mua-golovin.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhm-arsenal-nhan-hlv-unai-emery-hay-ngay-lap-tuc-mua-golovin-172-188557.html\">NHM Arsenal nh\u1eafn HLV Unai Emery: H\u00e3y ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c mua Golovin</span><br>\r\n<span>Arsenal mua Aleksandr Golovin, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3o NHM Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Saudi Arabia.</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-nga-50-saudi-arabia-diem-10-cho-aleksandr-golovin-421-188547.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/du-am-nga-50-saudi-arabia-diem-10-cho-aleksandr-golovin.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-nga-50-saudi-arabia-diem-10-cho-aleksandr-golovin-421-188547.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Nga 5-0 Saudi Arabia: \u0110i\u1ec3m 10 cho Aleksandr Golovin</span><br>\r\n<span>Tr\u1eadn Nga vs Saudi Arabia b\u1ea3ng A World Cup 2018, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Aleksandr Golovin \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5. Ch\u00ednh phong \u0111\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 22 tu\u1ed5i gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"343","checkdouble":"188906"},{"date":"10:57 19/06","title":"\"Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n C\u0110V Mexico \u0103n m\u1eebng t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ea5t\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/khong-the-co-chuyen-cdv-mexico-an-mung-tao-ra-dong-dat.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u C\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n qu\u1ed1c gia Mexico, kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n c\u00e1c C\u0110V Mexico \u0103n m\u1eebng t\u1ea1o n\u00ean \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng \u0110\u1ee9c.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u0110V Mexico t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ea5t<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/duc-vs-mexico-bang-f-463-188732.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">\u0110\u1ee9c vs Mexico</span></span> k\u1ebft th\u00fac, C\u01a1 quan gi\u00e1m s\u00e1t \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n Mexico (Simmsa)&nbsp; cho bi\u1ebft c\u00f3 hai c\u01a1n \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n \u1edf th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/sat-thu-lozano-noi-gi-sau-khi-choc-thung-luoi-dt-duc-421-188761.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">Hirving Lozano ghi b\u00e0n</span></span>. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u00e0 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u00fap Mexico \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 1-0.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CDV Mexico an mung tao ra dong dat.\" title=\"C\u0110V Mexico \u0103n m\u1eebng t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ea5t.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/khong-the-co-chuyen-cdv-mexico-an-mung-tao-ra-dong-dat.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>C\u0110V Mexico \u0103n m\u1eebng t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ea5t trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng \u0110\u1ee9c.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 l\u1ebd b\u1edfi qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0103n m\u1eebng n\u00ean Simmsa ghi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hai c\u01a1n rung ch\u1ea5n l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 2 \u0111\u1ed9 Richter. Vi\u1ec7c Mexico t\u1ea1o n\u00ean 2 c\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, c\u1ea3 theo ngh\u0129a \u0111en l\u1eabn ngh\u0129a b\u00f3ng khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Xyoli P\u00e9rez Campos, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u Trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n qu\u1ed1c gia Mexico (SSN) nghi ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 tr\u00ean: &quot;C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi, ho\u1eb7c m\u1ed9t nh\u00f3m ng\u01b0\u1eddi li\u00ean t\u1ee5c nh\u1ea3y g\u1ea7n m\u00e1y \u0111o t\u1ea1o n\u00ean k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Con ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u1ea3y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean rung ch\u1ea5n nh\u01b0ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ea5t&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">William Yeck, m\u1ed9t nh\u00e0 kh\u1ea3o s\u00e1t \u0111\u1ecba t\u1ea7ng c\u1ee7a Hoa K\u1ef3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1: &quot;D\u0129 nhi\u00ean con ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra c\u00e1c c\u01a1n rung ch\u1ea5n nh\u01b0ng trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p n\u00e0y l\u1ea1i kh\u00e1c. \u1ede \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1ec9 nh\u1ea3y \u0103n m\u1eebng th\u00ec kh\u00f3 t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 v\u1eady&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo William Yeck, con ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean c\u00e1c c\u01a1n \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n nh\u00e2n t\u1ea1o ch\u1ec9 b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ef1c m\u1ea1nh l\u00ean \u0111\u1ecba t\u1ea7ng. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng h\u1eefu h\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n nh\u01b0 khoan m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0o l\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5t khi th\u0103m d\u00f2 d\u1ea7u kh\u00ed, kho\u00e1ng s\u1ea3n,... ho\u1eb7c c\u00e1c v\u1ee5 th\u1eed h\u1ea1t nh\u00e2n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/cdv-mexico-tao-dong-dat-khi-mung-chien-tich-thang-duc-421-188800.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/cdv-mexico-tao-dong-dat-khi-mung-chien-tich-thang-duc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/cdv-mexico-tao-dong-dat-khi-mung-chien-tich-thang-duc-421-188800.html\">C\u0110V Mexico t\u1ea1o ... \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ea5t khi m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch th\u1eafng \u0110\u1ee9c</span><br>\r\nC\u01a1 quan gi\u00e1m s\u00e1t \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n Mexico (Simmsa) ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 hai c\u01a1n rung ch\u1ea5n \u1edf th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y, khi Lozano ghi b\u00e0n duy nh\u1ea5t trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"342","checkdouble":"188907"},{"date":"10:21 19/06","title":"Barca b\u1ecb sao Ajax n\u00f3i l\u1eddi cay \u0111\u1eafng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/de-jong-khong-muon-toi-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>De Jong kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Barca trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1ea7n. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf cho Andres Iniesta trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>C\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c thay th\u1ebf Iniesta</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nK\u1ebft th\u00fac m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18, Andres Iniesta \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay v\u1edbi Barcelona. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 34 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u01b0 x\u01b0a v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ea1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb. Iniesta kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u sau \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n sang Vissel Kobe c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, m\u1ed9t CLB c\u00f3 c\u00f9ng nh\u00e0 t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 v\u1edbi Barca.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia, h\u1ecd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i b\u1eaft tay v\u00e0o t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf. Trong danh s\u00e1ch n\u00e0y c\u00f3 h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f3 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng bao g\u1ed3m t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Frenkie de Jong c\u1ee7a Ajax. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi tr\u00f4i qua ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 21 tu\u1ed5i b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin d\u00f9ng \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i 1 CLB c\u00f3 ti\u1ebfng t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 Lan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"De Jong kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Barca trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1ea7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"De Jong kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Barca trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1ea7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/21/De-Jong-khong-muon-toi-Barca-trong-tuong-lai-gan-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Barca c\u1ea7n De Jong thay th\u1ebf Iniesta</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nDe Jong c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 22 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n (6 t\u1eeb gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb) v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 7 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. Nh\u1eefng t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n c\u1ea3 trong ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng l\u1eabn d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1eeb xa c\u1ee7a sao tr\u1ebb H\u00e0 Lan khi\u1ebfn Barca ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>B\u1ecb De Jong t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi t\u1edd Goal, De Jong kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Barca trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1ea7n. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p Blaugrana h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n anh l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p h\u1eefu \u00edch cho hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Barca.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Frenkie de Jong cua Ajax\" title=\"Frenkie de Jong cua Ajax\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/de-jong-khong-muon-toi-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">De Jong kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Barca trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c<em>Th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ecdc b\u00e1o T\u00e2y Ban Nha</em>\u201d, De Jong n\u00f3i. \u201c<em>\u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea5p thi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee9c t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i qu\u00e1 ch\u00fa t\u00e2m v\u00e0o n\u00f3. T\u00f4i giao n\u00f3 cho \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft li\u1ec7u \u00f4ng \u1ea5y c\u00f3 \u0111ang suy ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y hay kh\u00f4ng. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng.</em>\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i De Jong, Barca c\u0169ng \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi phong c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Trong \u0111\u00f3, ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u l\u00e0 Ilkay Gundogan c\u1ee7a Man City d\u00f9 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-muon-trao-doi-nguoi-voi-tottenham-180-188303.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/29/barca-muon-trao-doi-nguoi-voi-tottenham.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-muon-trao-doi-nguoi-voi-tottenham-180-188303.html\">Barca mu\u1ed1n trao \u0111\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1edbi Tottenham</span><br>\r\n<span>Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Christian Eriksen c\u1ee7a Tottenham, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn d\u00f9ng ti\u1ec1n c\u1ed9ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Rafinha \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Spurs nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/ivan-rakitic-noi-gi-truoc-vien-canh-neymar-cap-ben-real-madrid-180-188263.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/11/ivan-rakitic-noi-gi-truoc-vien-canh-neymar-cap-ben-real-madrid.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/ivan-rakitic-noi-gi-truoc-vien-canh-neymar-cap-ben-real-madrid-180-188263.html\">Ivan Rakitic n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh Neymar c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Real Madrid?</span><br>\r\n<span>Ivan Rakitic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Neymar, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 \u1edf Barca s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi PSG c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Real \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"341","checkdouble":"188908"}]}